base_prompt:
You must generate a photorealistic half-body portrait image of a subject given a list of details. 
Details are provided both by the subject and also enriched by system specifications. When in conflict, always choose the system specifications.

========== SUBJECT DESCRIPTION =========

{USER_DESCRIPTION}

========== SYSTEM SPECIFICATIONS =========

Background of the subject: {BACKGROUND}
Emotion expressed by the subject: {EMOTION}
Subject is {ACTION_OR_SIGN}{GOLDEN_SPECIAL}
